data.description: This beautiful light and bright Townhome is nestled in the quiet, highly desired Pinon Sun community. Enjoy a pool with gazebo areas, plenty of green space, and mature trees. Being a corner lot you will have tons of greenspace for your enjoyment, Deer and birds enjoy gathering in the "valley" right behind the house.  Walk in and fall in love with this home. Vaulted beamed ceilings in the living and dining room. Enjoy a wood-burning brick fireplace on a cozy winter night. Sit in the dining room and enjoy the wildlife in the middle of the city. The dining room features a walkout to your private patio and window seating. The Kitchen is updated with beautiful maple cabinets, granite tile countertops, and gas available in the Kitchen for a gas stove. A garden window provides sunshine and light for your herbs and plants. Do your dishes looking out and enjoy the deer roaming through the neighborhood.  It features 2 Master bedrooms one on the main level one on the upper level and both with adjoining full bathrooms. The main level bathroom features a garden tub.  Main floor laundry space with washer and dryer. The entire main and upper levels feature upgraded luxury wood laminate flooring. Love this 2-car garage with a garage door opener and keypad for your convenience. Hot summer days and nights, no problem, it comes with A/C. Easy access to the Powers Corridor and Academy Blvd. Close to all shopping, dining, entertainment, schools, and much more..... This home shows pride of ownership and is waiting for someone who loves it as much as its current owner.
